e:T7a7,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Inflection better than Microsoft Copilot?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Inflection scores 6.0 overall while Microsoft Copilot scores 7.0. Inflection is best for enterprise and custom AI assistants, while Microsoft Copilot excels for Office 365 users and enterprise."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Inflection or Microsoft Copilot?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Inflection starts at Enterprise and Microsoft Copilot starts at Free.  Microsoft Copilot offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Inflection to Microsoft Copilot?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Inflection and Microsoft Copilot support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Inflection vs Microsoft Copilot?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Inflection holds an overall rating of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10. Microsoft Copilot has an overall rating of 7/10 and ease of use score of 8/10. Users praise Inflection for enterprise-grade security and reliability and Microsoft Copilot for deep microsoft 365 integration."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Inflection or Microsoft Copilot?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Microsoft Copilot for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Inflection remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize enterprise-grade security and reliability. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"app